=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-b=
ottom: 0;"><strong>One-Wallet-One-Vote:</strong><span> Akin to direct democ=
racy, OWOV is an attempt to give an equal vote to each member. There are ch=
