x; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Quadratic Voting: </strong><span>M=
eant to decrease the voting power of large holders while still giving them =
more of a voice than smaller holders, QV increases the cost of each vote. O=
ne vote might cost one token, but two votes would cost four, three would co=
