 Masterworks Track Record is the dollar-weighted aggregate average change i=
n estimated fair market value of each issuer offered via the Masterworks pl=
atform on an annualized basis, excluding all offerings completed within the=
 last six months of the given performance period which we believe are not r=
eflective of Masterworks&#8217; performance, after deduction of all fees an=
